General.Name: ChinaEtek Service & Technology Co. Ltd.
General.Description: ChinaEtek Service & Technology Co., Ltd. provides third-party high-end IT infrastructure services in China. The company offers infrastructure consulting and planning services, such as infrastructure design, ITIL process consulting, information security consulting, and disaster backup consulting, which encompasses the design and planning for such units as minicomputer, PC server, storage devices, operating system, cluster, database, middleware, and virtual environment. It also provides IT infrastructure setup services consisting of system software development and virtualization; and designs and constructs SAN storage architecture, high-performance architecture, and network environment. In addition, the company offers IT infrastructure management and automation services, such as IT services management, monitoring automation, operation and maintenance automation, job scheduling automation, mainframe access control, and cloud resources management solutions. Further, it provides IT infrastructure maintenance services; and green equipment as servers and storage devices and related services. Additionally, the company offers EVO series products, which include assets management, cloud resources management, monitoring platform, and open platform mainframe access control solutions. It serves clients in banking, securities, insurance, telecommunications, transport and traffic, energy, manufacturing, government, and pharmaceutical industries. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in Beijing, China.
